gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 127, Jazz 124
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Jazz, 127-124. Tyrese Maxey recorded a new career-high 51 points (7-9 3PM) and two rebounds for the 76ers, with Tobias Harris adding 28 points, seven assists, and five rebounds in the victory. Lauri Markkanen tallied 28 points, 10 rebounds, and three assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 30-17, while the Jazz fall to 24-26.
